## gt mechanics / gotchas
- gt trunk = LOCAL master, which is ~175 commits behind origin/master and is
  checked out in the main worktree (/Users/andrew/conductor/weave) so it can't
  be fast-forwarded from here. gt therefore reports '175 commits' for this
  branch -- COSMETIC. The real base is origin/master: origin/master..HEAD == 1.
  `gt restack` would rebase onto STALE local master, so I rebased onto
  origin/master with plain git instead.
- Bash `grep` is ripgrep: `\\|` is literal, `-E`/`--include` error. Verify with
  the Grep tool. (This nearly produced false orphans earlier in the scan.)

